- scim needs non-POSIX and non-C locales, please generate locales first.
- add the following to your ~/.xinitrc:

	export XMODIFIERS=@im=SCIM
	export GTK_IM_MODULE="scim"
	export QT_IM_MODULE="scim"
	LANG=`your langauge` scim -d

- scim-pinyin is added. For other language support, file an issue at #6c37 .
